Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年的{\c&H00FFFF60}决心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.59,0:01:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗～到达下一个世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你噗什么噗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.39,0:01:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一直都在强调让你降落在一个好点的地方么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是幸好在海里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你开心的说什么傻话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.29,0:01:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主  有没有受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:02:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有点吓到了  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说是陆地了  连个岛都没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去我们四个人都要去见上帝了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:02:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了  坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把我称作坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着这张脸这么想也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不生气么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海上的男人怎么会在意那么小的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这艘Lagosta的船长唐巴尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是摩可拿  大家的偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么是么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  偶像是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界的领主好像是个好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以信他么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂不是一样的么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂那种东西不是没有善恶之分的么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊  不是很清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事情商量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的船上人手不太够呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们几个来做饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小摩可  加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:11.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会尽快完成的哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  新来的  快点打扫甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是新来的  我是黑钢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报上名来  是想打架么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  机关长在么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么小的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很聪明的孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操作引擎方面可比大人都强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎在哪里见过你吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我说了奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫小狼  让他来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是机关长  藤隆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸  爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.76,0:05:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以摸的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要试试看么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要试试看么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我刚才在想事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我再做一次给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:48.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再轻柔一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次要去发掘现场看看么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:07:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对考古有兴趣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲板扫除完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.61,0:07:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.65,0:07:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尝尝味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小摩可一起做的  叫做司寿的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是司寿  是寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好酸的味道啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还放着生的鱼～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.94,0:07:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法伊不喜欢寿司啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.92,0:07:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛有点酸酸的  但很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在和爸爸居住的国家里曾经吃过类似的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼爸爸是什么样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸很早就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.71,0:08:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子是小狼的爸爸么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严格的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是和小狼的爸爸有着同一个灵魂的另外一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么爸爸会比你还年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在异世界拥有同一灵魂的不同的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.46,0:08:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自身的年龄也未必相同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定在哪个世界有个小黑磷哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  这个国家有羽毛么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…完全没有这个感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又落空了么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  摩可拿还在这个世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是小狼这样想的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩可拿感觉到了小狼的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼想和那个孩子再待一下  哪怕一会会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以摩可拿会再待一下的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.75,0:09:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  摩可拿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我小狼就行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼在我这么大的时候做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮爸爸的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:10:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸是考古学家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼也是为了调查遗迹而出来旅行的么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然对考古学有兴趣  但是这并不是旅行的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有不管怎样都一定要找到的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有目标的人很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很想为什么而活着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要为什么而活  现在还在寻找这个目标
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也有这样的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那个老头在叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  船长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风的味道消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来暴风雨了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去是不行的  得关掉引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  必须要船长的命令才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.16,0:11:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去问一下  小狼请跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微把船稳住  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:56.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长  快点把引擎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机关长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君  藤隆君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼  抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机关长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑声
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.99,0:12:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君——
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  机关长  新来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像我们被冲到附近的岸上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lagosta号呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.31,0:13:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道沉没了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那样的话  会有更多船体的碎片漂上来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么船没事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先找到船  通知他们我们在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  好像沿着海走是不太可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们就去那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  这里是亡灵之岛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亡灵之岛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在岛上的亡灵们的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亡灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从先祖那里流传下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个岛上住着很恐怖的亡灵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们千万不能登陆那个岛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  小狼他们可能被冲到那个岛上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:09.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使那样  我们也没有办法救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.07,0:15:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行的人可能不能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是在这个国家生存的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须遵守先祖的叮嘱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样  请原谅我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…啊  不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说敬语了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我的话没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.25,0:15:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了  是亡灵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个岛上曾经住过人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是遗迹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是相当古老的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是岛的地图？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不要惧怕神的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倾听神的歌声之时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道路会变得光明」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能读懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经学过这种文字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「真正可怕的是…长的东西」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里就读不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条路看来是通向山顶的小路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看哪里都不像路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  有路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:17:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是爸爸教给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是「亡灵」的实体么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在听到的就是  刚才那遗迹上所写的神的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亡灵的笑声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:27.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是神的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是大家说的恐怖的亡灵的实体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都相信的亡灵  原来是风的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是船还在的话  应该在岛的另一面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:17:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到那边的话就只能穿过这个遗迹了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在遗迹里面要是遇到刚才那样的风怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不要惧怕神的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倾听神的歌声之时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道路会变得光明」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  听见这种歌声的时候就是安全的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们真的去岛那边了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船舵修理完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风向变了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才真危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着呢  两个人都活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.59,0:20:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看  两个人都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.81,0:20:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  马上就过来  等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.92,0:20:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「真正可怕的是…长的东西」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.57,0:20:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗迹上写的就是那个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.51,0:21:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许先祖是要借亡灵之说向我们传达  让我们小心那个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许亡灵的实体的确是那风声
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.68,0:21:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我以为那里是禁地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海还是很宽广的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.86,0:21:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使有上一件不可思议的事情也没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有及时去救你们真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了船长  我才找到了要找的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:40.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢诸位照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.58,0:21:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就在此分别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢  这里可是海上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩可拿·摩多基正兴奋不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.89,0:22:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.95,0:22:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小狼  我找到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.11,0:22:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长大以后我要成为考古学家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.80,0:22:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定能行的  绝对可以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.54,0:22:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.96,0:24:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有不亮的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.18,0:24:36.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的常识
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.42,0:24:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下一个世界好像完全行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.27,0:24:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有白天的这个国家里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.99,0:24:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待法伊的是孤零零的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.01,0:24:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？对法伊来说  那是很怀念的女孩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.86,0:24:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到法伊和那个女孩是怎样生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.94,0:24:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就请继续期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.58,0:24:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼·年代记
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.93,0:24:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与魔术师的约会
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.46,0:24:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回会为两位小女孩的登场而心动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:14.25,yingwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Far in the night,I can see it in every scene of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:17.09,yingwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}A tiny feather of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:27.97,yingwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I gotta go destiny never finds the way for me,my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.24,0:21:37.67,yingwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Even in the night I see your face,in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:44.11,yingwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}So I never lose my way to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:46.95,yingwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I never close my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:53.49,yingwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}The light is always there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.51,0:22:00.25,yingwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Time goes by,we can never stay the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.46,0:22:05.60,yingwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Now we come so far from love memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:11.12,yingwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Though your smile has gone,we will never be apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.36,0:22:16.96,yingwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}In our hearts we are one,for love melody.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.10,0:22:24.15,yingwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}The future arrives with your love.
